━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
§1 DATABASE: rminderdb (MariaDB 10.4, utf8mb4_general_ci)
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

TABLE users
  id            INT(11) PK AUTO_INCREMENT
  name          VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL
  email         VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL
  password      VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL          -- bcrypt new | MD5 legacy
  role          ENUM('admin','imam','leader','viewer') DEFAULT 'viewer'
  community_id  INT(11) DEFAULT NULL           -- 0 = admin/system; 1=Lagao;2=Bula;3=Uhaw
  status        ENUM('active','suspended','pending') DEFAULT 'active'  [migrate_additions]
DEMO ROWS:
  id=1  admin@email.com       MD5(admin)   role=admin   community_id=0
  id=7  alBallsani@email.com  MD5(123)     role=imam    community_id=2

TABLE communities
  id    INT(11) PK AUTO_INCREMENT
  name  VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL
  created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT current_timestamp()
ROWS: id=1 'Lagao (1st & 3rd)', id=2 'Bula', id=3 'Uhaw'

TABLE events
  id           INT(11) PK AUTO_INCREMENT
  title        VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL
  description  TEXT NOT NULL
  event_date   DATE NOT NULL
  event_time   TIME NOT NULL
  venue        VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL
  status       ENUM('upcoming','ongoing','completed') DEFAULT 'upcoming'
  created_at   TIMESTAMP DEFAULT current_timestamp()
  user_id      INT(11) DEFAULT NULL
  event_type   VARCHAR(20) DEFAULT 'personal'    -- 'personal' | 'system'
  visibility   VARCHAR(20) DEFAULT 'personal'    -- 'personal' | 'community'
  community_id INT(11) DEFAULT NULL              -- NULL = system event visible to all
NOTE: system events have event_type='system', user_id=0, community_id=NULL
NOTE: generateSystemEvents() seeds Iftar(18:00) Taraweeh(19:30) Suhoor(04:30) daily

TABLE announcements
  id           INT(11) PK AUTO_INCREMENT
  title        VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL
  message      TEXT NOT NULL
  user_id      INT(11) NOT NULL
  community_id INT(11) NOT NULL
  created_at   TIMESTAMP DEFAULT current_timestamp()
  category     ENUM('prayer_schedule','event_reminder','charity_drive','community_advisory') DEFAULT 'event_reminder'  [migrate]

TABLE donations
  id             INT(11) PK AUTO_INCREMENT
  donor_name     VARCHAR(255) DEFAULT NULL    -- defaults to 'Anonymous' in action
  donation_type  ENUM('cash','food','supplies') NOT NULL
  amount         DECIMAL(10,2) DEFAULT NULL   -- used when type=cash
  quantity       INT(11) DEFAULT NULL         -- used when type=food/supplies
  remarks        TEXT DEFAULT NULL
  community_id   INT(11) DEFAULT NULL
  user_id        INT(11) DEFAULT NULL
  created_at     TIMESTAMP DEFAULT current_timestamp()

TABLE distributions
  id             INT(11) PK AUTO_INCREMENT
  donation_id    INT(11) DEFAULT NULL         -- FK → donations.id (no constraint enforced)
  beneficiary    VARCHAR(255) DEFAULT NULL
  item_name      VARCHAR(255) DEFAULT NULL
  quantity       INT(11) DEFAULT NULL
  distributed_at DATE DEFAULT NULL
  user_id        INT(11) DEFAULT NULL
  community_id   INT(11) DEFAULT NULL
  created_at     TIMESTAMP DEFAULT current_timestamp()

TABLE attendance  [added by migrate_additions]
  id           INT(11) PK AUTO_INCREMENT
  event_id     INT(11) NOT NULL               -- FK → events.id (no constraint enforced)
  name         VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL
  status       ENUM('present','absent') DEFAULT 'present'
  recorded_by  INT(11) DEFAULT NULL           -- FK → users.id
  community_id INT(11) DEFAULT NULL
  created_at   TIMESTAMP DEFAULT current_timestamp()

TABLE forum_threads  [added by migrate_additions]
  id           INT(11) PK AUTO_INCREMENT
  title        VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL
  body         TEXT NOT NULL
  user_id      INT(11) NOT NULL
  community_id INT(11) DEFAULT NULL           -- NULL = cross-community / pinned global
  is_pinned    TINYINT(1) DEFAULT 0
  created_at   TIMESTAMP DEFAULT current_timestamp()

TABLE forum_replies  [added by migrate_additions]
  id         INT(11) PK AUTO_INCREMENT
  thread_id  INT(11) NOT NULL                 -- FK → forum_threads.id
  user_id    INT(11) NOT NULL
  body       TEXT NOT NULL
  created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT current_timestamp()

TABLE audit_logs  [added by migrate_additions]
  id         INT(11) PK AUTO_INCREMENT
  user_id    INT(11) NOT NULL
  action     VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL  -- 'DONATION_RECORDED','EVENT_DELETED','USER_SUSPENDED','USER_ACTIVE','APPOINTMENT_APPROVED/REJECTED/COMPLETED'
  details    TEXT DEFAULT NULL
  created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP()
LOGGER: include "../functions/logger.php" then call logActivity($conn, $user_id, $action, $details)
LOGGED IN: add_donation.php, delete_event.php, update_appointment.php, pages/users.php toggle

TABLE appointments  [added by migrate_additions]
  id             INT(11) PK AUTO_INCREMENT
  reference_no   VARCHAR(30) NOT NULL UNIQUE  -- format: MCAD-YYYYMMDD-NNN
  full_name      VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL
  contact        VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL
  email          VARCHAR(255) DEFAULT NULL
  service_type   ENUM('islamic_marriage','halal_certification','burial_assistance','scholarship') NOT NULL
  preferred_date DATE NOT NULL
  preferred_time TIME NOT NULL
  purpose        TEXT DEFAULT NULL
  status         ENUM('pending','approved','rejected','completed') DEFAULT 'pending'
  admin_remarks  TEXT DEFAULT NULL
  created_at     TIMESTAMP DEFAULT current_timestamp()

